<h4 class="western"><span style="color: #080809;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><b>The Truth: 16 Fully Funded Programs</b></span></span></span></h4>
Despite the CCC cut, <strong>16 programs remain fully funded</strong>—yes, <strong>FULLY FUNDED</strong>—and they’re ready to support communities, including kids in schools. Here’s the list:
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Fresh Fruit and Vegetable Program (FOR SCHOOLS)</strong></li>
