 	<li><strong>Special Milk Program (FOR SCHOOLS)</strong></li>
 	<li><strong>Summer Food Service Program (FOR KIDS AND TEENS AT SCHOOLS AND OUTSIDE OF SCHOOLS)</strong></li>
